le/TNDM/111%2c%e7%b0%a1%2c1307%2c20220519%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TNDM,111,簡,1307,20220519,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"簡","JNO":"1307","JDATE":"20220519","JTITLE":"違反毒品危害防制條例"}